Global Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis Drugs Market Insights
Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis Drugs Market size was valued at USD 1.11 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.01 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis Drugs Market Overview
The global Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS) drugs market is valued at approximately USD 4.5 billion in 2025 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.8% from 2025 to 2035. This market is driven by increasing incidences of ALS and growing awareness about the disease. The availability of various treatment options and novel drug developments are also contributing factors to the market's growth. The demand for advanced therapies is anticipated to surge with the rise in personalized medicine approaches and advancements in ALS research.

